src/
├── app/                  (if using Next.js App Router)
│   ├── (auth)/           ← Group all auth routes here
│   │   ├── login/
│   │   │   └── page.tsx
│   │   ├── signup/
│   │   │   └── page.tsx
│   │   └── layout.tsx    (optional: shared auth layout, e.g. no navbar)
│   ├── admin/            ← Later for admin pages
│   ├── bikes/
│   ├── page.tsx          ← Home
│   └── layout.tsx        ← Main layout with navbar
│
├── components/
│   ├── ui/               ← Reusable UI (Button, Input, Card, etc.)
│   ├── AuthForm.tsx      ← Shared form component for login/signup
│   ├── Navbar.tsx
│   ├── BikeCard.tsx
│   └── ...               ← Other content components
│
└── lib/ or utils/        ← Auth helpers, API calls, etc.